'''''Orcim''''' was a [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] that transferred munitions to the [[Dellalt system/Legends|Dellalt system]], preparing the [[Operation Strike Fear]]. It was destroyed by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] and [[Hamo Blastwell]] during the defection of ''[[Bixby]]''.

